### TIER 3: Structural Changes (Long-term)

#### 6. Tiered Maintenance Pricing

**Concept:** Scale costs with bot tier/wins

```
Scavenger Class (0-2 wins):
  Recharge: 0.06 ICP
  Repair: 0.03 ICP

Raider Class (3-5 wins):
  Recharge: 0.08 ICP
  Repair: 0.04 ICP

Elite Class (6-9 wins):
  Recharge: 0.10 ICP
  Repair: 0.05 ICP

SilentKlan Class (10+ wins):
  Recharge: 0.12 ICP
  Repair: 0.06 ICP
```

**Rationale:**
- New players pay less, reducing barrier to entry
- Elite bots earn more, can afford higher costs
- Matches prize pool progression

**Impact:**
- Better new player experience
- Elite players unaffected (already profitable)
- Natural progression curve

