1. **Improve Value** â†’ Maintenance restores more (+12-13%)
2. **Improve Visibility** â†’ Economics dashboard shows total earnings
3. **Balance Scavenging** â†’ Reduce parts 15%, increase battery costs 15%
4. **Net Result** â†’ All strategies remain profitable, better perceived value

**Why This Works:**
- âœ… Addresses "expensive maintenance" perception
- âœ… Maintains profitability across all playstyles
- âœ… Balances racing vs scavenging incentives
